    <item>
      <title>爱尔兰将提前举行大选，哈里斯民调领先</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-06/ireland-to-hold-early-election-as-harris-pounces-on-poll-lead</link>
      <description><![CDATA[爱尔兰将提前举行大选，总理西蒙·哈里斯将利用有利的民意调查数据和主要反对党新芬党支持率的下降来争取选举胜利。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-06/ireland-to-hold-early-election-as-harris-pounces-on-poll-lead</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 06 Nov 2024 18:50:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>哈里斯已要求特朗普承认败选</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-06/harris-has-called-trump-to-concede-election</link>
      <description><![CDATA[副总统的一位高级助手向彭博社表示，卡马拉·哈里斯已致电唐纳德·特朗普，要求其承认自己胜选。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-06/harris-has-called-trump-to-concede-election</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 06 Nov 2024 18:50:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>哈里斯的失败让美国女性 248 年来的障碍得以维系</title>
