    <item>
      <title>欧洲央行行长维勒鲁瓦称特朗普当选对全球经济构成风险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-06/ecb-s-villeroy-says-trump-election-poses-risks-to-global-economy</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法国央行行长弗朗索瓦·维勒鲁瓦德加洛表示，唐纳德·特朗普当选为下一任美国总统将给全球经济带来风险和不确定性，并应鼓励欧洲解决其弱点。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-06/ecb-s-villeroy-says-trump-election-poses-risks-to-global-economy</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 06 Nov 2024 18:27:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国财政部高级官员否认该部门违法</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-06/top-uk-treasury-official-rejects-suggestion-department-broke-law</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国财政大臣雷切尔·里夫斯的高级官员否认了财政部公务员向政府财政监管机构隐瞒数十亿英镑公共财政黑洞信息而违法的说法，但承认他们确实违反了行为准则。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-06/top-uk-treasury-official-rejects-suggestion-department-broke-law</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 06 Nov 2024 18:17:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>唐纳德·特朗普有办法在第二任期内解雇强大的金融监管机构</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-06/trump-has-tools-to-fire-powerful-consumer-financial-regulator-in-second-term</link>
      <description><![CDATA[罗希特·乔普拉 (Rohit Chopra) 对非法收回汽车、取消抵押品赎回权和银行透支费用的严厉打击，使他成为消费者群体心目中的英雄和放贷者的敌人。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-06/trump-has-tools-to-fire-powerful-consumer-financial-regulator-in-second-term</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 06 Nov 2024 18:08:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普的胜利对 MAGA 运动意味着什么</title>
