    <item>
      <title>特朗普重返白宫后民粹主义被释放</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/features/2024-11-06/trump-2024-election-win-how-populist-politics-won-the-white-house</link>
      <description><![CDATA[这场决定性的胜利表明特朗普的第一任期并非偶然。现在，他已经完全掌握了白宫的行政权力，并拥有更多的自由来随心所欲地治理国家。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/features/2024-11-06/trump-2024-election-win-how-populist-politics-won-the-white-house</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 06 Nov 2024 11:30:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
